# Ebonveil
#
# Philosophy: track reproducibility (manifest, profiles, tools, docs).
# Never track mod binaries, downloads, or secrets.

# --- Secrets / local env ---
# Nexus key is read from env NEXUS_API_KEY or secrets/nexus_api_key.txt (ADR 0010).
# .env is not used by any script, but stays ignored as a defensive net.
.env
.env.*
*.apikey
nexus_api_key.txt
secrets/

# --- Caches ---
.cache/
*.log
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# --- MO2 portable binary tree (bootstrap regenerates) ---
# Allowlist approach: ignore mo2/** then un-ignore profiles & tracked configs.
mo2/**
!mo2/profiles/
!mo2/profiles/**
# Live ModOrganizer.ini is machine-specific + rewritten by MO2 constantly; track the
# sanitized template instead and regenerate via tools/configure-mo2.ps1 (ADR 0009).
!mo2/ModOrganizer.ini.template
!mo2/categories.dat
!mo2/explorer++.ini
!mo2/portable.txt

# --- MO2 downloads selection cache (local) ---
mo2/downloads/.ebonveil-resolved.json

# --- OS / editor ---
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# --- Temp extraction ---
*.tmp
*.7z
!tools/**/*.ps1
